		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just get &quot;An unexpected error has occurred&quot; for those Mouser links.<br /><br />The encoder chip in an NES controller is a 4021 parallel to serial shift register, and <a href="http://infiniteneslives.com/products.php" class="postlink">infiniteneslives.com</a> sells 4021s extracted from NES controllers whose encoder has been replaced with the encoder for a different platform.

		

